Book overview

COVALENT The Organic Chemistry Revision Book for JEE, NEET & State Boards, in collaboration with Sankalp Jauhari.

 Target Exams: JEE Main, JEE Advanced, NEET UG, and all State Board Exams
 Covers: Entire Organic Chemistry Syllabus of Class 11 & 12 including all Name Reactions, Mechanisms, and Conceptual Tricks

 What Makes COVALENT Different?
  • Mechanism-Focused Learning: Visual diagrams explain the 5 key mechanisms that unlock 90% of Organic Chemistry questions.
  • All Important Name Reactions Covered: Each reaction is clearly labelled and diagrammed for fast recall.
  • Revision-First Structure: No textbook fluff. Only exam-relevant concepts, arranged logically.
  • Colorful & Intuitive Layout: Diagrams, exception boxes, and comparison tables make Organic Chemistry fun and easy to retain.
  • Quick Hybridisation, Conjugation, GOC Tips: Smart shortcuts that help crack JEE/NEET logic in seconds.

 Inside the Book:
  • Structured by Concept Flow not dry chapters
  • Shortcut Boxes, Mistake Alerts, and Final Summary Pages
  • Full-color pages with visual reaction maps
  • Includes bonus Test with Vibes section for last-minute revision

 Who Should Use This Book?
If you're a student preparing for JEE, NEET, or Class 11/12 Boards and want to revise smarter, not harder this is for you.

 Trusted by toppers. Designed by Organic Chemistry experts. Printed with premium quality.

Product Description

Built from Real Struggles, Solved with Smart Design

Sankalp Jauhari shared a vision: make Organic Chemistry easier, visual, and logical for JEE aspirants. That vision helped shape COVALENT into what students actually need.

COVALENT The Organic Chemistry Revolution Students Deserve

COVALENT isnt just a book its a breakthrough. From clear diagrams to shortcut tables, from basics to advanced mechanisms every page is designed to help you revise faster and remember longer.

This is how Organic Chemistry should have always looked.

Concept-First Organic, Finally Done Right

Tired of memorising reactions before understanding them? COVALENT flips the script. It starts where true learning begins logic, not chapter numbers.

Understand the why behind every mechanism, before diving into the what.

When Concepts Are Clear, Everything Else Clicks.

COVALENT isnt just about hybridisation its about finally understanding Organic Chemistry. From confusing basics to tough mechanisms, every topic is broken down with clear visuals, mistake alerts, and smart logic.

It doesnt just teach reactions it builds your foundation, step by step.

Bonus Youll Actually Use Free Reagent Chart Included!

Get instant access to the most exam-relevant reagent summary organised by chapter, designed for rapid recall.

Created with care by Sankalp Jauhari, this chart is a game-changer for JEE & NEET Organic revision.
